  "title": "Registered Architect (Technical Director)",
  "description": "<p>Bayes is representing an Engineering Consultancy on a Director-level QP Architect role. The role leads Building projects in the Singapore market</p><ul><li>The role requires a BOA (Registered in Singapore), Architectural Masters/Degree, from Engineering Consultancy or Design/Architectural Practice with above 15 years of senior-level experience</li><li>Building/Property/Commercial Projects – To provide technical leadership and governance, supporting work winning, design, and multi-disciplinary delivery.</li><li>Managing budgets and risks, and ensuring high-quality delivery while balancing client and internal needs.</li><li>Act as the key point of accountability, aligning client requirements with technical execution and team performance.</li><li>Identify and secure new business opportunities to support the consultancy’s growth in allocated market for Building/Property/Commercial</li></ul><p>If the role resonates with you and your professional experience complements the responsibilities listed, send your resume to <strong>koh.dickson@bayesrecruitment.com</strong><br /><br />Dickson Koh, EA Registration R1103367<br /><br />www.bayesrecruitment.com</p>",
